Requirements:

- Go 1.5: http://golang.org/doc/install
- git 2.3 or higher: http://www.git-scm.com
- libgit2 0.23: https://libgit2.github.com
- make 3.7 or greater: https://www.gnu.org/software/make/
- export GO15VENDOREXPERIMENT=1


Installation:

- Run `make install` to build and install the project

Configuration:

- $DESTDIR sets the base installation directory. Default is /usr/local
- $DESTBIN sets the binary installation directory. Default is $DESTDIR/bin
- $DESTMAN sets the manual installation directory. Default is
  $DESTDIR/share/man/man1

- $INSTALLCMD installs files. Default is "install -C" (BSD-style)
- $INSTALLDIRCMD installs directories. Default is "install -d" (BSD-style)
